These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-1::.
House: cape-cod, modern
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: february, july
1. the modern house is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| House           | modern | cape-cod |
| Birthday   | july     | february  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-2::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, december
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: snowboarding, handball
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |
| Birthday         | december   | march      |
| Sport   | snowboarding | handball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-3::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: red, green
2 different games are played: billiard, mah-jongg
1. the person who likes red is somewhere to the right of the person playing billiard##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2    |
| Color   | green | red    |
| Game     | billiard | mah-jongg |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta
The people have 2 different jobs:  videographer, manager
1. the manager is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |
| Beverage   | cola   | fanta |
| Job   | videographer | manager |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-5::.
2 different pets are kept: dog, fish
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: orchid, marigold
1. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the right of the person who growsmarigold##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |
| Pet   | fish | dog |
| Flower     | marigold    | orchid    |

